data.description: Welcome to 1038 Shore Line Dr, located in Woodland Lakes Subdivision in sought after Oldham County. This home features a first floor primary with a spacious walk in closet. As you enter the home, you enter into the 2 story living room. The pass through to the kitchen opens up the space and allows you to be connected to others in the next room. The living room features a gas fireplace, perfect for cozy cool evenings. The newly installed vinyl plank floors run through the living room, into the kitchen. The kitchen also features a second story high ceiling, giving such a spacious, grand feel to the room. The kitchen island offers extra storage and prep space. Off the kitchen is the back deck featuring a view of the nature conservatory that backs up to the property. The back yard features a fence and storage shed, perfect for storing larger lawn equipment. As you ascend the stairs to the second floor you will notice the newly installed hardwood treads and spindles. Upstairs is 2 spacious bedrooms along with a full bath. Home is located just outside downtown LaGrange where you can spend the afternoon shopping local artisan shops and eateries. Oldham County features award winning schools and is just a hop skip and a jump from Louisville. Come see this great home today!
